3. cs.SY (Systems and Control) - The paper considers the effect of circuit cost on the performance of the multiple-access channel, which is a topic that falls under systems and control. 
4. cs.MM (Multimedia) - The paper discusses the transmission of data over a multiple-access channel, which is a topic that falls under multimedia.
